%H A108039 V. I. Arnold, <a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1215/S0012-7094-91-06323-4">Bernoulli-Euler updown numbers associated with function singularities, their combinatorics and arithmetics</a>, Duke Math. J. 63 (1991), 537-555.
